 Juliet: Dawn of Justness]]\".}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Astra Logue]]\n| Olivia Swann\n| \"[[Terms of Service (Legends of Tomorrow)|Terms of Service]]\"\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Anti-Monitor|Mobius / Anti-Monitor]]\n| [[LaMonica Garrett]]\n| \"[[Crisis on Infinite Earths (Arrowverse)|Crisis on Infinite Earths: Part Five]]\"\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}{{efn|Garrett is only credited in the main cast in \"[[Crisis on Infinite Earths|Crisis on Infinite Earths: Part Five]].\"}}\n|-\n| colspan=\"8\" style=\"background-color:#ccccff;\" | Recurring characters\n<!-- The following all appear in 4 or more episodes across one season, defined for this series as recurring. -->\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Vandal Savage (Arrowverse)|Vandal Savage]]\n| [[Casper Crump]]\n| \"Pilot, Part 1\"\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CNone}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Damien Darhk (Arrowverse)|Damien Darhk]]\n| [[Neal McDonough]]\n| \"[[Pilot, Part 2]]\"\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Zaman Druce]]\n| [[Martin Donovan]]\n| \"[[White Knights (Legends of Tomorrow)|White Knights]]\"\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Lily Stein]]\n| Christina Brucato\n| \"[[Outlaw Country (Legends of Tomorrow)|Outlaw Country]]\"\n| {{CNone}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Malcolm Merlyn (Arrowverse)|Malcolm Merlyn / Dark Archer]]\n| [[John Barrowman]]\n| \"[[The Chicago Way]]\"\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Hank Heywood (Arrowverse)|Henry \"Hank\" Heywood, Jr.]]\n| Patrick Lubczyk\n| \"[[Moonshot (Legends of Tomorrow)|Moonshot]]\"\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest