ard Snart (Arrowverse)|Leonard Snart / Captain Cold]]\n| [[Wentworth Miller]]\n| {{CMain|Main}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CGuest}}{{efn|Miller portrays his character's Earth-X counterpart [[Leo Snart]] in season three.}}\n! colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Eobard Thawne (Arrowverse)|Eobard Thawne / Reverse Flash]]\n| [[Matt Letscher]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | \"[[Out of Time (Legends of Tomorrow)|Out of Time]]\"\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Amaya Jiwe|Amaya Jiwe / Vixen]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Maisie Richardson-Sellers]]\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CNone}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Charlie (Arrowverse)|Charlie / Clotho]]\n| \"[[Dancing Queen (Legends of Tomorrow)|Dancing Queen]]\"\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CMain|Main}}{{efn|Sellers is credited as a special guest star in her first appearance as Charlie then as a main cast member from \"[[Wet Hot American Bummer]]\" onward.}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Nate Heywood (Arrowverse)|Nate Heywood / Steel]]\n| [[Nick Zano]]\n| \"Out of Time\"\n| {{CNone}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Zari Tomaz]]\n| [[Tala Ashe]]\n| \"[[Zari (Legends of Tomorrow episode)|Zari]]\"\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Wally West (Arrowverse)|Wally West / Kid Flash]]\n| [[Keiynan Lonsdale]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | \"[[Aruba-Con]]\"\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CMain|Main}}{{efn|Lonsdale is first credited as a main actor in \"[[The Curse of the Earth Totem]]\" after previously making guest appearances in \"[[Aruba-Con]]\" and \"[[Here I Go Again (Legends of Tomorrow)|Here I Go Again]]\".}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Ava Sharpe]]\n| [[Jes Macallan]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[John Constantine (Arrowverse)|John Constantine]]\n| [[Matt Ryan (actor)|Matt Ryan]]\n| \"[[Beebo the God of War]]\"\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CMain|Main}}{{efn|Ryan is listed among the main cast but credited in the opening titles as special appearance.}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Mona Wu]]\n| [[Ramona Young]]\n| \"Dancing Queen\"\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Nora Darhk]]\n| [[Courtney Ford]]\n| \"[[Return of the Mack (Legends of Tomorrow)|Return of the Mack]]\"\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CMain|Main}}{{efn|Ford is credited through \"[[Romeo v Juliet: Dawn of Justness]]\".}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Astra Logue]]\n| Olivia Swann\n| \"[[Terms of Service (Legends of Tomorrow)|Terms of Service]]\"\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Anti-Monitor|Mobius / Anti-Monitor]]\n| [[LaMonica Garrett]]\n| \"[[Crisis on Infinite Earths (Arrowverse)|Crisis on Infinite Earths: Part Five]]\"\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}{{efn|Garrett is only credited in the main cast in \"[[Crisis on Infinite Earths|Crisis on Infinite Earths: Part Five]].\"}}\n|-\n| colspan=\"8\" style=\"background-color:#ccccff;\" | Recurring characters\n<!-- The following all appear in 4 or more episodes across one season, defined for this series as recurring. -->\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Vandal Savage (Arrowverse)|Vandal Savage]]\n| [[Casper Crump]]\n| \"Pilot, Part 1\"\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CNone}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Damien Darhk (Arrowverse)|Damien Darhk]]\n| [[Neal McDonough]]\n| \"[[Pilot, Part 2]]\"\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Zaman Druce]]\n| [[Martin Donovan]]\n| \"[[White Knights (Legends of Tomorrow)|White Knights]]\"\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\"